origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "Insurance.compare_loan_rates",
        "description": "比较定期寿险和终身寿险的贷款利率，返回比较结果。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "term_life_rate",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "定期寿险的贷款利率。"
            },
            {
                "name": "whole_life_rate",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "终身寿险的贷款利率。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison",
                "description": "贷款利率的比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_term_life_loan_rate",
        "description": "获取定期寿险的贷款利率。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "rate",
                "description": "定期寿险的贷款利率。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_whole_life_loan_rate",
        "description": "获取终身寿险的贷款利率。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "rate",
                "description": "终身寿险的贷款利率。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.recommend_policy",
        "description": "根据贷款利率比较结果和资金需求，推荐合适的保险政策。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "comparison",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "贷款利率的比较结果。"
            },
            {
                "name": "fund_need",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "资金需求描述。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "recommendation",
                "description": "推荐的保险政策。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.calculate_premium",
        "description": "根据保险类型和保额计算保险费用。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "insurance_type",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险类型（如定期寿险、终身寿险等）。"
            },
            {
                "name": "coverage_amount",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "保额。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "premium",
                "description": "计算出的保险费用。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_policy_details",
        "description": "获取特定保险政策的详细信息。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "policy_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险政策的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "details",
                "description": "保险政策的详细信息。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.check_eligibility",
        "description": "检查用户是否符合特定保险政策的资格要求。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "user_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "用户的唯一标识符。"
            },
            {
                "name": "policy_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "保险政策的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "eligibility",
                "description": "用户是否符合资格的结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_available_policies",
        "description": "获取当前可用的所有保险政策列表。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "policies",
                "description": "可用的保险政策列表。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
